msgid "Advanced Mode"
msgstr "進階模式"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:56
msgid ""
"Most users will never need to switch to the `Advanced` tab, but if you need "
"to customize any of the video encoding settings, for example, custom "
"bitrates, different codecs, or limiting the range of frames exported, this "
"is the tab for you."
msgstr "大多數使用者不需要切換到 `進階` 標籤頁，但若您需要自訂影片編碼設定，例如自訂位元率、不同編碼器，或限制匯出幀範圍，這裡是您的選擇。"

